<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				padding: 40px;
				color: #1a1a1a;
				font-size: 14px;
			}
			.craftmanHeader {
				display: flex;
				justify-content: space-between;
				align-items: flex-start;
				margin-bottom: 30px;
				padding-bottom: 20px;
				border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
			}
			.craftmanHeader h2 {
				margin: 0 0 8px;
				font-size: 1.4rem;
			}
			.craftmanHeader p {
				margin: 3px 0;
				color: #555;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
			}
			.craftmanLogo {
				max-height: 80px;
				object-fit: contain;
			}
			h1 {
				font-size: 1.8rem;
				margin-bottom: 5px;
			}
			.billMeta {
				display: flex;
				gap: 30px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				color: #666;
				font-size: 0.95rem;
			}
			.box {
				background: #f5f5f5;
				padding: 15px;
				border-radius: 8px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
			}
			.box h3 {
				margin: 0 0 8px;
			}
			table {
				width: 100%;
				border-collapse: collapse;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
			}
			th {
				background: #1a1a1a;
				color: white;
				padding: 10px;
				text-align: left;
			}
			td {
				padding: 10px;
				border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
			}
			.estimateNb {
				text-align: right;
			}
			.totals {
				text-align: right;
				margin-bottom: 30px;
			}
			.totals p {
				margin: 5px 0;
			}
			.legalMentions {
				margin-top: 40px;
				padding-top: 15px;
				border-top: 1px solid #eee;
				font-size: 0.75rem;
				color: #999;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="craftmanHeader">
			<div>
				<h2>{{ craftman.socialReason }}</h2>
				<p>{{ craftman.mail }}</p>
				<p>{{ craftman.proAdress }},
					{{ craftman.postCode }}
					{{ craftman.city }}</p>
				<p>SIRET :
					{{ craftman.SIRET }}</p>
			</div>
			{% if craftman.logo_url %}
				<img src="{{ craftman.logo_url }}" alt="Logo" class="craftmanLogo">
			{% endif %}
		</div>

		<h1>FACTURE
			{{ bill.reference }}</h1>

		<div class="billMeta">
			<p>Date d'émission :
				{{ bill.created_at|date("d/m/Y") }}</p>
			<p>Statut :
				{{ bill.status_bill }}</p>
		</div>

		<div class="box">
			<h3>Client</h3>
			{% if bill.client %}
				<p>{{ bill.client.firstName }}
					{{ bill.client.lastName }}</p>
			{% else %}
				<p>Aucun client assigné</p>
			{% endif %}
		</div>

		<table>
			<thead>
				<tr>
					<th>Description</th>
					<th>Qté</th>
					<th>Prix unitaire</th>
					<th>Total</th>
				</tr>
			</thead>
			<tbody>
				{% for line in bill.billLine %}
					<tr>
						<td>{{ line.description }}</td>
						<td class="estimateNb">{{ line.qty }}</td>
						<td class="estimateNb">{{ line.unitAmount|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }}
							€</td>
						<td class="estimateNb">{{ line.lineTotal|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }}
							€</td>
					</tr>
				{% endfor %}
			</tbody>
		</table>

		<div class="totals">
			<p>Total HT :
				{{ totalHT|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }}
				€</p>
			<p>TVA ({{ bill.tva }}%) :
				{{ montantTVA|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }}
				€</p>
			<p>
				<strong>Total TTC :
					{{ totalTTC|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }}
					€</strong>
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="legalMentions">
			<p>En cas de retard de paiement, une pénalité de 3 fois le taux d'intérêt légal sera appliquée.</p>
			<p>Indemnité forfaitaire pour frais de recouvrement : 40 €</p>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
